{"id":149006,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/卡扎菲幼子在北约空袭中丧生/","date":"2011-05-01T10:30:20Z","modified":"2011-05-01T10:30:20Z","title":"卡扎菲幼子在北约空袭中丧生","content":"<div>\n<p>的黎波里<br />据利比亚政府公布的消息，该国领导人卡扎菲的幼子赛义夫周六夜间在一次空袭中丧生，卡扎菲的3个孙子也死于空袭。利比亚政府发言人易卜拉欣称，卡扎菲本人和他的妻子当时也在赛义夫的住宅中，但没有受伤。易卜拉欣称,此次空袭是以杀害该国领导人为目的的有目标的袭击，是违反国际法的。北约证实周六空袭了的黎波里一处指挥所。北约指挥官布沙尔强调，空袭的所有目标均为军事目标，并与卡扎菲政权对平民的军事攻击有关。此前北约拒绝了卡扎菲提出的谈判建议。赛义夫死于空袭的消息传出后，在反叛武装中心班加西，人们鸣枪以示庆贺。目前，忠于卡扎菲的军队夺取了以南300公里处的绿洲城市扎罗。</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15042124%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%8D%A1%E6%89%8E%E8%8F%B2%E5%B9%BC%E5%AD%90%E5%9C%A8%E5%8C%97%E7%BA%A6%E7%A9%BA%E8%A2%AD%E4%B8%AD%E4%B8%A7%E7%94%9F\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[15483]}